On Wednesday, October 23, 1996,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        ELRON INFORMATION TECHNOLOGIES (E.I.T.) by 
                        ELRON ELECTRONIC INDUSTRIES LTD., Haifa 31015.
                        The USPTO has given the ELRON INFORMATION TECHNOLOGIES (E.I.T.) 
                        trademark serial  number of  75185897.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - FAILURE TO RESPOND OR LATE RESPONSE.
                        The correspondent listed for ELRON INFORMATION TECHNOLOGIES (E.I.T.) is 
                        
                        
                                            RONIT GILLON of 
                                            COBRIN GITTES & SAMUEL,  750 LEXINGTON AVENUE, NEW YORK NY  10022 
                                .
                            The ELRON INFORMATION TECHNOLOGIES (E.I.T.) trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Communications Services
                                , 
                                    Education and Entertainment Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for ELRON INFORMATION TECHNOLOGIES (E.I.T.) 
                            is valve-added telecommunications services, namely, local area network, interconnections, telex messages transfer, facsimile messages transfer, electronic mail and EDI services, database access, data communication, network, management and customer support. 
                            





